{"tid":921871,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"差估署10月私宅售價指數按月跌逾2%　連挫3個月","createTime":"2018-11-30T02:15:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-30T03:46:01.000Z","uid":28245,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2728afbbcdb631804d340eefe8fd679fe2355c89","tid":921871,"uid":28245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T02:15:41.000Z","msg":"差餉物業估價署公布的最新數據顯示，截至今年10月私人住宅售價指數報380.3點，按月大跌約2.36%，已連挫3個月。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同場加映<br />\n<br />\n今年最低！翔龍灣兩房售600萬　較高位冧價27%<br />\n<br />\n市場消息指出，土瓜灣翔龍灣6座底層B室，實用面積385方呎，兩房間隔，原以720萬港元放售，經多次減價後以600萬元易手，呎價15,584元，售價及低價均為今年低位。 <br />\n<br />\n資料顯示，對上一宗同面積成交為10月登記售出的5座低層G室，作價830萬元，呎價21,558元，以此計算，最新個案大幅跌價230萬元，相差約27.7%。代理指出，翔龍灣買賣膠着，上述為本月首宗成交個案。 <br />\n<br />\n下個月個指數仲精彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8643af34d414906e004d127bdc2711ef99f2f53","tid":921871,"uid":35965,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T02:36:47.000Z","msg":"假跌<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d460d46b3e91cc70103fc0427ea21a27db178b5c","tid":921871,"uid":56698,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T02:37:30.000Z","msg":"冇毒果吹得咁勁囉 跌兩成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df310658331bf49b36b8eb4b91da5b886e6f2165","tid":921871,"uid":35965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d460d46b3e91cc70103fc0427ea21a27db178b5c","tid":921871,"uid":56698,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T02:37:30.000Z","msg":"冇毒果吹得咁勁囉 跌兩成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T02:42:46.000Z","msg":"&quot;某d 屋苑&quot;由高位計,呎價係跌咗兩成"},{"pid":"2d803c30bcf3ffee8a1ecbfd9ad8a814f95b4882","tid":921871,"uid":140516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T02:51:15.000Z","msg":"真心問 咁係咪會減差餉?"},{"pid":"1350f235664